data.title: Capital Region Mah Jongg
data.meta_description: We are a relaxed Mah Jongg group for new to experienced players. We use the National Mah Jongg League card and rules. Although we play a casual game we do not give lessons. Perspective MEMBERS NEED to post A CURRENT PHOTO AND BRIEF PROFILE when requesting membership.
data.text:
Our Group:

We're a women's group for "Mature" players. All players must be fully vaccinated against COVID-19, and remain current with further vaccines, if needed, for variants.

Bring your current American MJ card.

Arrive at 2:00. We'll play as soon as we have 3 or 4 players( depending on how many RSVPS we have). Play ends at 4:30. Please cancel by Tuesday night if your plans change.

Check the web page before arriving on Wednesday in case of last minute cancellations.
